  stimulus_text = 'The author of the passage states that the novel "The Great Gatsby" is about "the difficulty of realizing the American Dream." The author continues that "the novel explores the themes of wealth, love, and loss, and it shows how difficult it can be to achieve happiness and success." The author concludes by saying that "the novel is ultimately a tragic story about the unattainable nature of the American Dream."',
