UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The author of the article suggests that the current economic climate is characterized by both opportunity and uncertainty.  One of the main points is that the rise in the popularity of online shopping is an example of this uncertainty. The author explains that consumers are constantly trying to predict how prices will fluctuate, and that this leads to a great deal of anxiety.  Another of the author’s main points is that the increase in the use of e-commerce is an example of the opportunities presented by the new economic climate. The author suggests that the ability of businesses to reach a wider audience through online platforms is a major advantage that is helping to drive economic growth. The author concludes the article by arguing that businesses need to be aware of both the opportunities and the challenges of the new economic climate in order to succeed.  Which of the following choices best describes the main idea of the article?',
